content.content: Collateral Onboarding Call #32: Gnosis - Wednesday, June 16 17:00 UTC  Gnosis1287×720 93.8 KB  Time in your local-timezone format: 2021-06-16T17:00:00Z Mark it on your Google Calendar!  Dial In Details Zoom call Passcode: ONBOARD  Intro An open discussion where we discuss projects and potential assets for MCD, open for anyone to join. If you’d like to present, check out this thread.  Agenda  Intro by @juan. Presentation by @StefanGeorge.   Gnosis - https://gnosis.io/  MIP6: [GNO] Collateral Onboarding Application  GNO is the governance token of GnosisDAO, which was launched November 23rd 2020. The GnosisDAO is giving GNO holders direct stake in Gnosis’ strategic decision making and fund management. Via token-weighted voting, GNO holders may participate in core roadmap decisions of Gnosis’ core product lines. Funding of projects and other initiatives are made available only for proposals approved by a majority of GNO token holders.
